						<div class="postbody">Well, this is obviously just an oversight of the designers. I don't think that it has the in-universe meaning of &quot;He isn't really a Catholic.&quot;<br /><br />Back when &quot;Castlevania III&quot; came out, the Belmonts were probably intended as people who fight for the church.<br />(They were driven out of the land by the people out of fear, but the old games don't mention anything about excommunication, so it was just some stupidity from the superstitious common folk, not a papal decision like it is shown in the anime.)</div>

					
